[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "姉様、こっちは準備完了",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_036_01294",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ん、あんがと。ベップは仕事が速いし正確だし、\nいつも助かるわ～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01295",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "一家に一台、ベップをよろしく……嘘。\nベップは姉様の元にしか存在しない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_036_01296",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "さーて、ベスティラ王曰く、次の「九偉人図」は\nピルッツァ島なんだよね……キノコで有名なとこ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01297",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "諸島同盟に入ってない、ちょっと遠い島だけど……\n姉様、大丈夫？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_036_01298",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ああ、うん。いけるいける。\nオーベンランドみたいな辺境に行くわけでもないし？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01299",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "とはいえ、いちいちこんなこと考えてるようじゃ\nまた暗黒の氷海に行くときは厳しいかもなあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01300",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "姉様……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_036_01301",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "なんてね！\n大丈夫だよ、空き時間を使って色々と模索中だから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01302",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "アルビーナ、いるか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01303",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "エルスさん？\nこんな遅くなのにまだ捜査を？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01304",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "監察官に休みの時間などない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01305",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ふわあぁぁ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01306",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "見事なあくび、島魚を丸呑みできそう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_036_01307",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "まったく……立ち寄ったのは他でもない。\nあの二人について、詳しく話を聞かせてもらいたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01308",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ヤドヴィガとキューンといったな？\nあれはなんだ？　ただ者ではなさすぎるぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01309",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "アルビーナさんが探している「九偉人図」と関連が\nあるんですよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01310",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "……エルスさん相手にすっとぼけるのは無理だよね。\n分かりました、お話しします",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01311",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "人々を導くパルメ族……その配下であるホムンクルス\n九偉人……ヴァレリアやイェルカも同じ存在……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01312",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "情報の洪水です……もう頭がくらくら……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01313",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "にわかには信じがたいが……その話が真実だとすると\nこれまで諸島同盟であった未解決事件も辻褄が合う……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01314",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "指導者の死亡で紛争が終了したあの件も、あの件も……\n九偉人の自称管理によるものと考えると、ぞっとするな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01315",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "タイニーはともかく、エルスさんもすんなり\n信じてくれたのはちょっと意外だったかも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01316",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "アタシが話を聞いた時は、固まっちゃったというか\n",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01317",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "実際に彼女らの力を目の当たりにしてしまったら\n信じないわけにもいかないさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01318",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "……だが、あの管理とやらは諸島の秩序を乱す行為だ。\n我々の監察下でパルメ族の勝手を許すわけにはいかない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01319",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "我々には我々の秩序がある。\n自分たちの世界は自分たちで良くしていかねばならん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01320",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "おお、さすが。言い切るっすね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01321",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "しかし相手は強大だ。こうなるとこちらも\n強力な味方が欲しいな……ジョゼを引き込むか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01322",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あの仮面の賞金稼ぎを、ですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01323",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ボス、いつも監察官に引き抜こうとして\n断られてるじゃないですか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01324",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "まあそうだが、今回は事態が事態だ。\n監察官への抜擢ではなく共同戦線という形ならば……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01325",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "でも、あんな怪しい仮面の人、信頼できるんすか？\nきっとジョゼって名前も偽名っすよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01326",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "いけ好かない言動で腹が立つことはある。\nだが、腹と同じくらい腕が立つのも確かだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01327",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "妙な格好でも、妙な真似をする奴じゃない。\nそれくらいは、調べがついているさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01328",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "……好評、絶賛",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_036_01329",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "尊敬するボスの評価ではあるけど……変てこ仮面さん、\nちゃらんぽらんな人だと思うけどなぁ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01330",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]